<TEXT>
<P>
 TEMPLE CITY: City Hall will be closed on alternate Fridays beginning Jan. 21 
to comply with air district requirements. City Hall and Civic Center Building 
hours Monday through Thursday will be extended from 8 a.m. to 6 p.m. Both 
buildings will be open on alternate Fridays from 8 a.m. to 5 p.m. 
</P>
