<HEADLINE>
<P>
TO OUR READERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today's Westside section offers a colorful new package of local news and 
features.The new magazine-style section, which will appear every Thursday and 
Sunday, contains cover stories of widespread interest, community news, topical 
reports on areas of special importance and listings of events. 
</P>
<P>
 On Thursdays, there will be a wrap-up of local sports news. Inserted in 
Sunday's edition will be the Westside real estate advertising section, offering 
listings for homes, property and open houses. 
</P>
