<P>
FOR TEENS; SEEN AT SCHOOL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Kirsten Carr, 17, of Arcadia High School, dresses for comfort and looks for 
flexibility. 
</P>
<P>
 Clothes: "I look for comfort and I have to be warm when it's cold. But today, 
I'm definitely going for comfortable. I like green and blue (clothes). I'm kind 
of a Limited Express person. I like flannels and sweat shirts." 
</P>
<P>
 Shoes: "(I like) something that goes with a lot of clothes, something I can 
wear with a lot of things." 
</P>
<P>
 Accessories: "I'm not much of a jewelry person except for special occasions." 
About the backpack: "I had never seen anything like it. I thought it was 
different." 
</P>
