</P>
<P>
 This L.A. band has been getting good notices on the indie-alternative scene. 
The show on Friday, Jan. 14, also features Riverside's Discothi-Q and the O.C. 
band, Poastal. It continues the promising alternative rock series at the 
comfortable new bar and coffeehouse Our House. (714) 650-8960. 
</P>
