</P>
<P>
 The Chantays were still teens working up guitar licks in their bedrooms when 
they came up with "Pipeline." Composers Bob Spickard and Brian Carman are still 
in the band, which will celebrate the 30th anniversary of the surf classic's 
release at Randell's on Sunday, Jan. 16. (714) 556-7700. CAPTION on live pg.4 
</P>
