<P>
Column; Recording Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011394-0169 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 003582 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 13, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
