<DOCNO> LA011394-0236 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 003649 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 13, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 5; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
