<HEADLINE>
<P>
DAVID NOVAK TO CLOSE STORYTELLING FESTIVAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Beverly Hills Public Library's Family Storytelling Festival series ends 
Sunday with a performance by noted storyteller David Novak, who uses mime and 
circus techniques while telling original stories, fables and myths. 
</P>
<P>
 Tickets are $5 per child, $7 per adult. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (310) 288-2201. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011394-0337 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 003750 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 13, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
